      <h1>Learn and Get Educated</h1>
      <p class="subtitle">Give the team a base level of training so everyone understands how FTC works before building starts.</p>
      <section class="content-section">
        <p>Use this stage to teach the team the basics of robot design, code structure, safety, scouting, and how matches are scored.</p>
        <div class="content-subsection">
          <h3>Training ideas</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Watch FTC game and rules videos together</li>
            <li>Introduce beginner programming and CAD lessons</li>
            <li>Review electrical and mechanical safety</li>
            <li>Practice note-taking and scouting basics</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <p><strong>Action:</strong> Set up a weekly learning session so the team grows skills while the launch is still in progress.</p>
